<th scope="row">Born</th>
<td>1557 <a href="/wiki/Anno_Mundi" title="Anno Mundi">AM</a><sup id="cite_ref-am_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-am-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup><br />
(date disputed)<sup id="cite_ref-am_1-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-am-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
